# Bar, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Bar () is a rural locality (a selo) in Mukhorshibirsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 466 as of 2010. There are 18 streets.
Geography
Bar is located 37&nbsp;km northwest of Mukhorshibir (the district's administrative centre) by road. Khoshun-Uzur is the nearest rural locality.
